#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:2
msgid "Core"
msgstr "Core"

#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:17
msgid ""
"The :mod:`qilisdk.core` layer underpins both the digital and analog "
"stacks. It provides symbolic variables, optimization models, sparse "
"quantum tensors, and the "
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable` mixin used "
"throughout the SDK."
msgstr ""
"La capa :mod:`qilisdk.core` és la base tant de les piles digital com "
"analògica. Proporciona variables simbòliques, models d'optimització, "
"tensors quàntics dispersos i el mixin "
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable` utilitzat arreu "
"del SDK."

#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:21
msgid "Highlights:"
msgstr "Aspectes destacats:"

#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:23
msgid ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.variables` supplies binary, spin, continuous, and "
"parameter variables plus algebraic helpers "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Term`, comparison factories, encodings)."
msgstr ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.variables` proporciona variables binàries, de spin, "
"contínues i de paràmetre, a més d'assistents algebraics "
"(:class:`~qilisdk.core.variables.Term`, fàbriques de comparació, codificacions)."

#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:26
msgid ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.model` builds constrained optimization programs and "
"offers tools to automatically convert the model to "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO` format if the constraints are linear."
msgstr ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.model` construeix programes d'optimització amb "
"restriccions i ofereix eines per convertir automàticament el model al "
"format :class:`~qilisdk.core.model.QUBO` si les restriccions són lineals."

#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:28
msgid ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor` manages sparse quantum objects and utilities"
" such as :func:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.tensor_prod` and "
":func:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.expect_val`."
msgstr ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor` gestiona objectes quàntics dispersos i "
"utilitats com :func:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.tensor_prod` i "
":func:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.expect_val`."

#: ../../modules/core/core.rst:30
msgid ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable` standardizes how "
"objects expose symbolic parameters (shared by circuits, schedules, etc.)."
msgstr ""
":mod:`~qilisdk.core.parameterizable.Parameterizable` estandarditza la "
"manera com els objectes exposen paràmetres simbòlics (compartits per "
"circuits, esquemes, etc.)."

